@startuml
!theme plain
title 01. Inference SLO Composition
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "Workload classes" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "SLO policy" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "Tier policy" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "Coherence-CE" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Scheduler gates" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : TTFT/TPOT
N2 --> N3 : cache hit ratio
N3 --> N4 : latency class
N4 --> N5 : rollout criteria

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
